    OK, CRIME FIGHTERS,
    WE HAVE A TRIPLE HOMICIDE

03:09.190 --> 03:10.822
    IN SALT LAKE CITY, UTAH.
    A COUPLE,

03:10.824 --> 03:13.258
    RON AND KAREN MYERSON
    WERE FOUND SHOT TO DEATH

03:13.260 --> 03:14.393
    IN THEIR HOME 4 HOURS AGO.

03:14.395 --> 03:16.862
    SEVERAL HOURS BEFORE THAT,
    A SECURITY GUARD

03:16.864 --> 03:19.831
WAS FOUND STABBED TO DEATH
AT A SMALL OFFICE BUILDING.

03:19.833 --> 03:21.900
    AND LET ME GUESS--
    THE GUN USED
    TO SHOOT THE COUPLE

03:21.902 --> 03:25.270
GET YOUR MUG OUT
'CAUSE COFFEE
IS FOR CLOSERS.

03:25.272 --> 03:27.372
        NO SIGN OF A BREAK-IN
        OR FORCED ENTRY.

03:27.374 --> 03:28.874
            MAYBE THE COUPLE
            KNEW THE UNSUB.

03:28.876 --> 03:33.845
    BUT IT WOULDN'T HAVE
    TAKEN HIM HOURS
    TO GET TO THEIR HOUSE.

03:33.847 --> 03:35.214
        WHAT WAS HE DOING
        IN THE MEANTIME?

03:35.216 --> 03:36.615
    WATCHING THE COUPLE,
    CONDUCTING SURVEILLANCE,

03:36.617 --> 03:39.351
    OR HE ENCOUNTERED THEM
    EARLIER AND WAS
    TORTURING THEM.

03:39.353 --> 03:41.620
        BUT THE M.E.
        AND THE POLICE BOTH SAY
        THERE WAS NO EVIDENCE

03:41.622 --> 03:45.424
ONE THING IS CLEAR.
BOTH CRIME SCENES
LOOK CHAOTIC.

03:45.426 --> 03:46.992
THIS UNSUB IS DISORGANIZED.

03:46.994 --> 03:49.895
    THE CHAOS COULD MEAN
    THAT THIS UNSUB
    IS EITHER PSYCHOTIC

03:49.897 --> 03:52.264
    OR UNDER SOME TIME PRESSURE.
    AND IMPROVISING.

03:52.266 --> 03:54.600
        HE MAY FEEL KILLING'S
        HIS ONLY OPTION.

03:54.602 --> 03:56.301
            WE MAY BE LOOKING
            AT A SPREE.

03:56.303 --> 03:57.369
WHEELS UP IN 30.

04:05.478 --> 04:07.879
            HEY, HURRY UP!

04:13.319 --> 04:15.387
YOU CAN PUT THAT AWAY.

04:15.389 --> 04:16.788
I TOLD YOU I'D HELP YOU.

04:16.790 --> 04:19.291
        COME ON, LET'S GO.

04:20.560 --> 04:22.427
            LISTEN.

04:22.429 --> 04:25.764
        YOU NEED TO CALM DOWN.

04:25.766 --> 04:29.334
        YOU DID NOT HAVE
        TO KILL THAT COUPLE
        OR THAT SECURITY GUARD.

04:29.336 --> 04:31.370
            YOU WERE LEAVING
            A TRAIL OF BODIES

04:31.372 --> 04:34.573
            BECAUSE YOU CAN'T
            KEEP IT TOGETHER.

04:35.441 --> 04:36.942
    SHUT UP.

04:36.944 --> 04:39.311
    GET IN.

04:44.951 --> 04:49.488
        LOOK, YOU MIGHT AS WELL
        JUST DRAW A ROAD MAP
        FOR THE COPS.

04:51.391 --> 04:54.760
HAVE YOU EVER
LOOKED DEATH IN THE EYE?

04:55.428 --> 04:56.695
'CAUSE I HAVE.

04:56.697 --> 04:58.664
AND I'VE SEEN
THE GRIM REAPER

04:58.666 --> 05:01.833
STARING RIGHT BACK AT ME.

05:06.472 --> 05:09.941
    WE SHOULD WAIT TILL
    IT'S DARK BEFORE WE LEAVE.

