06:20.080 --> 06:24.683
    RON'S BEEN TO RENO 4 TIMES
    IN THE LAST FEW MONTHS.

06:24.685 --> 06:29.955
        BUT WOULD A PROFESSIONAL
        KILLER MURDER A SECURITY
        GUARD FOR A WEAPON?

06:29.957 --> 06:32.791
WELL, BASED ON
THE DISORGANIZATION
OF THE KILLS,

06:32.793 --> 06:34.426
